sub_title: Industrial Engineer | SAP SuccessFactors Consultant | MSc. International Management
summary:
Engineer with a strong background and always eager to learn and develop new skills. 

Analytical and critical thinker, passionate about solving problems with innovative tools and working in teams.

Active learning always has been part of my journey, therefore I finished my master International Management last year, which have provided me with new skillsets and has enabled me to develop innovative strategies. 

Currently exploring methods to analyze data during my master’s in Applied Data Science, interested in the impact data has in current society and daily life.
